00:09:50.950 --> 00:09:55.230
nano seconds ago. 5 to 6 nanoseconds in the past.

00:09:55.230 --> 00:09:58.250
Of course, a delay that brief is pretty
much undetectable

00:09:58.250 --> 00:10:01.880
